Meta, Google, Amazon, Microsoft




2022-2024 Ensign College
2025 Sep - now BYU-Idaho



Mar 2025 - Jun 2025 Family Search | Technical Intern, Remote, USA

Developed a Python script using BeautifulSoup to extract over 13,000 rows and 156,000 cells of structured data from external websites. Replaced a repetitive manual copy-paste process, estimated at 120+ hours of human effort, with a single-click automation, significantly improving speed, accuracy, and scalability.

Used pandas to implement functionality such as fixing encodin

Apr 2024 -  Jun 2025 Murdock InfoTech | Web Developer Intern, Remote, USA

Developed an IVR system using Twilio’s Voice API, customers can navigate menus through voice or keypad inputs
Utilized Node.js to log call data, which was later processed for performance analysis and improving customer interactions
Authored YAML configuration files and Dockerized the app
